  "note": [
    "The text has a long history of adaptation into different languages, all seemingly adapted from the story Kitāb Bilawhar wa-Yūdāsaf ( Būd̲h̲āsaf ). The origins and original languages of the story are contested: the proposals are that the Arabic versions, of which this Christian version in AR320 is one, came into Arabic from Pahlavi or from Central Asian Manicheans (writing in New Persian in Manichean script)."
  ],
